### API ENDPOINT TESTING SUITE
# Requires the VS Code Extension: "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
# Click the little "Send Request" button dynamically generated physically above each block explicitly!

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7511/api/v1/auth
@email = testing_integration@example.com
@password = strongpassword123
@username = automated_tester_user

### =======================================
### 1. REGISTER NEW ACCOUNT dynamically
### =======================================
# Will logically dispatch an explicit actual live email natively.
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}


### =======================================
### 2. VERIFY EMAIL (OTP REQUIRED!)
### =======================================
# ⚠️ REPLACE '123456' with the physical active code logically received natively in your official inbox!
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "otp": "123456"
}


### =======================================
### 3. LOGIN EFFECTIVELY inherently
### =======================================
# (Automatically assigns dynamic underlying secure HTTP cookies mathematically efficiently)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### >>> Capture dynamic JWT smoothly implicitly explicitly
@access_token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}


### =======================================
### 4. FETCH PROFILE PAYLOAD
### =======================================
# Retrieves specifically protected generic profile seamlessly logically utilizing Bearer tokens actively.
GET {{baseUrl}}/get-me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### =======================================
### 5. FETCH ACTIVE SESSIONS
### =======================================
# Retrieves a clean structured array natively outlining every active IP / Browser user agent natively effectively linked physically explicitly!
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### =======================================
### 6. REFRESH ABSTRACT TOKENS
### =======================================
# Functionally forces standard rotation natively logically dynamically utilizing strict HTTP-cookies abstractly cleanly!
GET {{baseUrl}}/refresh-token


### =======================================
### 7. LOGOUT SECURELY (WIPE ALL DEVICES)
### =======================================
# Mathematically revokes ALL specific underlying session footprints directly explicitly natively!
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout-all
